  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Also at 1st level, you can thunderously rebuke attackers. When a creature within <strong>5 feet</strong> of you that you can see hits you with an attack, you can use your <strong>reaction </strong>to cause the creature to make a <strong>Dexterity saving throw</strong>. The creature takes 2d8 lightning or thunder damage (your choice) on a failed saving throw, and half as much damage on a successful one.</p>\n<p>You can use this feature a number of times equal to your Wisdom modifier (a minimum of once). You regain all expended uses when you finish a long rest.</p>",
